== 評價 ==
《叛逆暗殺》被[[國家評論協會|美國國家評論協會]]選為2007年[[國家評論協會獎十大電影|十大電影]]之一，凱西·艾佛列克同時奪得[[國家評論協會獎最佳男配角|最佳男配角]]。<ref>{{cite news | author= | url=http://www.msnbc.msn.com/id/22116897/ | title=Board names ‘No Country’ best film of ’07 | publisher=[[MSNBC|MSNBC]] | date=2007-12-05 | accessdate=2007-12-05 | archive-date=2007-12-07 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071207163051/http://www.msnbc.msn.com/id/22116897/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>電影於[[奧斯卡金像獎|奧斯卡金像獎]]獲得2項提名，包括[[奧斯卡最佳男配角獎|最佳男配角]]和[[奧斯卡最佳攝影獎|最佳攝影]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.oscars.org/80academyawards/nominees/index.html |title=Nominees - 80th Annual Academy Awards |accessdate=2008-01-22 |publisher=Academy of Motion Picture Arts and Sciences |archive-date=2008-01-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080123152423/http://www.oscars.org/80academyawards/nominees/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，亦於[[金球獎|金球獎]]取得1項[[奧斯卡最佳男配角獎|最佳男配角]]提名。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.goldenglobes.org/news/id/81 |title=HOLLYWOOD FOREIGN PRESS ASSOCIATION 2008 GOLDEN GLOBE AWARDS FOR THE YEAR ENDED DECEMBER 31, 2007 |accessdate=2007-12-17 |date=2007-12-13 |publisher=goldenglobes.org |archive-date=2007-12-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071215072618/http://www.goldenglobes.org/news/id/81 |dead-url=no }}</ref>
